 ---

-The closest ancestor with `position: absolute`.
+`bg-green`

 ---

-The `<body>` element.
+`float`

 #### --answer--

-The closest positioned ancestor with `position` set to `relative`, `absolute`, or `fixed`.
+`z-index`

